net.proteusframework.ui.miwt.component.composite

Class TabbedContainerImpl

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.proteusframework.ui.miwt.component.ComponentImpl
      • net.proteusframework.ui.miwt.component.Container
        • net.proteusframework.ui.miwt.component.composite.TabbedContainerImpl
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    PropertyChangeListener, Iterable<Component>, EventListener, LocaleContextSource, Component, TabbedContainer, ListCellRenderer, ParentComponent, TableCellRenderer, TreeCellRenderer, ListSelectionListener

    public class TabbedContainerImpl
extends Container
implements ListSelectionListener, TabbedContainer

    The TabbedContainer provides a CardContainer controlled by a Tabs. The different cards can be selected using the tabs.

    The drag source and drop target setters are delegated to the Tabs.

    Author:
    Pat B. Double (double@i2rd.com), Russ Tennant (russ@i2rd.com)
